This file contains the release notes of Pamela for Android.
For more info see http://0x20.be/Pamela_for_Android

== Version 0.4 ==
2011-03-13

* Min API level to 4, android 1.6.
* Changed app name to pamela.client2 with new keystore as the original password was lost.

== Version 0.3 ==
2010-11-15

* Fixed tab height.
* Added additional options to the menu (although they don't work yet).

== Version 0.2 ==
2010-11-11

* Added tab interface.
* Added hsbxl occupants list.
* Removed redundant library.

== Version 0.1 ==
2010-11-11

* Initial release displaying the 0x20 occupants in a list with a refresh button.